Actually,  protect a program on Sun only using gethostid() function is easy
to break. The number is in the PROM, but you can change this function
to return any other number that you prefer. You only must to know 
the 'hostid' of the licensed machine and applied it. 

Exist other methos most sophisticated to protect correctly software on Sun 
against ilegal use.

